<br>
They can't continue to be 100% Warrior and 100% Caster, if that is where they still are.  They used to be 100% Warrior and 40% Caster. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/upankrat.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pankrat</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble Squire</span><br>  Posts: 23<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(6/6/02 10:14:20 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=366.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> re: Casters AI</span><hr size=1> Respectfully disagree Sir Lage,<br>
