Even with improved AI, AI will always be vastly inferior to RI (real intelligence =p). There will be quickly discernable patterns and players will always come up with strategies and tactics to work around them. If you had caster NPC's that hit in the 15's and less than 2k HP every caster mob in the game would be uber trivial. <br>
